# HIREINBOX - Claude Code

**Mission:** AI CV screening for SA SMEs | **Stack:** Next.js 16 + TypeScript + Supabase

## Critical Rules
⚠️ **UNIFIED AI BRAIN:** ALWAYS use `SA_CONTEXT_PROMPT` from `/src/lib/sa-context.ts` - NEVER standalone AI
⚠️ **NO TAILWIND** - Use inline CSS only
⚠️ **Polish before ship** - We have just begun
⚠️ **Prefer editing existing files** over creating new ones

## Standards
- SA-specific: CA(SA), BCom, local companies
- POPIA compliant, evidence-based
- Respectful language: "not successful" not "rejected"
- AI assists, human decides final actions
- No emojis unless requested

## Status
**Real:** CV screening (fine-tuned), video analysis, pilot pages
**Mockups:** Headhunter search, talent hub, reference check, AI interview

## Key Locations
- `/src/app/pilot/` - Pilot dashboard/screening/talent-mapping/reports
- `/src/lib/sa-context.ts` - SA intelligence (use for ALL AI features)
- `/src/app/api/` - API routes

## Commands
`npm run dev` (port 3002) | `/clear` saves tokens | Email: hello@hireinbox.co.za
